Package: hypersonicIntercept
Title: Predictive Modeling for Hypersonic Missile Interception
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Rega", "Mullen", email = "user@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    An R package providing statistical models and predictive analytics for 
    analyzing hypersonic missile interception success rates. Implements 
    logistic regression models examining relationships between missile speed 
    characteristics (Mach number, hypersonic designation) and interception outcomes.
